					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>This is a verse in praise of the sword of Adigaṉ called also Adiyamāṉ Viḍugādaḻagiya Perumāḷ (the Chēra chief of Tagaḍūr) who won a victory in battle against the Koṅgu army. His ensign of power <hi rend="italic">viz.</hi>, a parasol (?) and a <hi rend="italic">chāmara</hi> (flywhisk) are engraved below the inscription.</p>						

						</summary>
