<lb n="1"/>ceṅkuca<unclear>t</unclear>ti niraṭaittuc ceṅ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>koṭu ceṟupaṭṭu vaṅkaḷuṟu ko
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇṭuḻutu velvitaittuk
<lb n="4" break="no"/>koṅkar piṇa nāṟuṭaiya
<lb n="5"/>paṟikkak kaṇṭatevar kai ma
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇ nāṟun tāratikaṉ vāḷ
